{"word":"H6761 - צֶלַע - tselaʻ - tseh'-lah - Adversity","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צֶלַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>tselaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>tseh'-lah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Adversity"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஆபத்து, தவறிவிழுதல், தடுமாறி விழுதல் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"limping, stumbling"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H6760 - צָלַע - tsâlaʻ - tsaw-lah'/6760\">H6760</a>; a <i>limping</i> or <i>fall</i> (figuratively): - adversity, halt (-ing)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6760 - צָלַע - tsâlaʻ - tsaw-lah'/6760\">H6760</a>, <a href=\"#/H6761 - צֶלַע - tselaʻ - tseh'-lah/6761\">H6761</a>, <a href=\"#/H6764 - צָלָף - Tsâlâph - tsaw-lawf'/6764\">H6764</a>, <a href=\"#/H6765 - צְלׇפְחָד - Tsᵉlophchâd - tsel-of-chawd'/6765\">H6765</a>, <a href=\"#/H6766 - צֶלְצַח - Tseltsach - tsel-tsakh'/6766\">H6766</a>, <a href=\"#/H6768 - צֶלֶק - Tseleq - tseh'-lek/6768\">H6768</a>"}]}